Document: AudioStreamRandomizer
Path: godot/classes/class_audiostreamrandomizer.rst
Summary: A control node that randomizes audio playback properties.

AudioStreamRandomizer

Inherits: AudioStream < Resource < RefCounted < Object

A control node that randomizes audio playback properties.

This node takes one or more AudioStream resources and plays one of them randomly. It also allows for randomization of pitch and volume.

Properties:
  random_pitch (float): The range of pitch randomization. Default: 0.0.
  random_volume (float): The range of volume randomization. Default: 0.0.
  streams (Array[AudioStream]): The array of AudioStream resources to choose from.

Methods:
  play(from_pos: float = 0.0) → void: Plays the stream.
  stop() → void: Stops the stream.
---CHUNK---
